		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Small tip, I didn't realise until way late in the game. If you jump (try doing it from a high location to get more air time) and then take out your bow you'll slow down time while aiming giving you a little extra time to go for the air. The slowdown ends when you land, of course.

		

