		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Both midair aiming and shield surfing have in-game tutorials. The former is mandatory to reach Vah Medoh. There's also a list of controls in the menu (the one you use to save/load, not the E-manual).<br /><br />None of which makes the layout any less confusing.

		

